1775844947589168	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE3oww		item.create	bn-2qbr	{"description":"bn-2ury surfaced that the shipped bn binary is built with [profile.release] opt-level=\"z\" (size-optimized). Every perf win in this pass (pagerank 25x, full_rebuild 2x, normalize 2.9x) was measured under [profile.bench] which I pinned to opt-level=3. End users running the release build pay a 30-60% runtime penalty on top of everything else, independently of the hot-path wins.\n\n**Trade-off**\n- opt-level=z → smaller binary, slower code (current).\n- opt-level=3 + lto=thin → ~5-15% larger binary (typically 500KB-2MB on a bn-sized tool), 30-60% faster runtime on CPU-bound paths.\n\n**Why this needs a bone + your approval**\nThis changes the end-user binary, not just measurement infra. bn-2ury added [profile.release-fast] as a non-breaking alternative, but the default release path still ships opt-level=z. Flipping the default is a visible user-facing change — worth filing and discussing rather than slipping in.\n\n**Plan**\n1. Build bn under both profiles, compare stripped binary size on disk.\n2. Run the existing criterion benches twice — under [profile.bench] (already speed-optimized, should be unchanged) and under [profile.release] modified to opt-level=3 — to confirm the speedup is real on this specific codebase, not just folk knowledge.\n3. If the size delta is acceptable (e.g., < 2 MB): flip [profile.release] to opt-level=3 lto=thin codegen-units=16, keep panic=abort strip=true. Delete [profile.release-fast] since it's now redundant.\n4. If the size delta is unacceptable: close this bone with the measurements and keep release-fast as the installable-via-flag option, documented in README.\n\n**Exit**\nEither a merged flip with before/after binary size and bench numbers, or a written close with the trade-off numbers so the next person doesn't have to re-measure.","kind":"task","labels":["perf","release"],"parent":"bn-1582","size":"xs","title":"Flip [profile.release] from opt-level=\"z\" to opt-level=3","urgency":"urgent"}	blake3:fFU2GjdJJ5LxexdzM3Sh8rMPnr6LxA7XLkYG9QwO7b4
1775844955778845	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE3pAw		item.move	bn-2qbr	{"state":"doing"}	blake3:psyw8sYcI-6ccH1MjlBt9k8u-iEV1SXKPenmcoV2bcQ
