1777164452406685	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE3sww		item.create	bn-1s5m	{"description":"Follow-up to b5964301. Three issues:\n1. SearchView tier-2 thread now wipes tier-1 results when semantic refinement fails (changed return; -> Vec::new()). Restore non-destructive failure: only send merged results when there is something useful, otherwise leave tier-1 visible.\n2. merge_direct_id_matches in search.rs only promotes rank<=1 direct-id matches above ranked results, but list/data.rs ranks 'contains-id' (rank 2) above title-contains. Make search.rs match: promote all id-matching direct hits (rank<=2) above ranked, leave only the title fallback (rank 3) at the tail. (rank 3 doesn't actually exist in direct_id_matches output, so effectively all direct hits go in the front block.)\n3. tracing::debug! on hybrid_search_fast errors hides real backend failures from default logs — bump to warn!.","kind":"task","title":"fix TUI search regressions from id-match patch"}	blake3:myRpkG3k4Hv-lN8GnYBgcxE42_hvTYZx2h_Rc853O6Y
